{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_10_01_short",
  "title": "兵藤雫 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『劇団★見』結成後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、ここは……もう少し、動作を大きくした方が\n映えるかも……もう一回やってみよう",
      "startTime": 8.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　{user}さん、お疲れ様、です\nごめんなさい、集中してて気付かなかった……",
      "startTime": 17.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "雫も演技の練習、お疲れ様\n劇団★見での活動、始めてみてどうだ？",
      "startTime": 23.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "すっごく、楽しい……！\nでも、やることも考えることも一杯で、大変",
      "startTime": 29.9074147225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "どの演目をやるのか決める時も……\nみんなと一緒に、凄く悩んだ",
      "startTime": 38.1740813892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、すずちゃんと偶然本屋さんで会って……\nお互いに好きなお話が一緒で、ちゃんと選べた",
      "startTime": 45.2018596251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "大変だけど、一人じゃないから\n充実してて、楽しい",
      "startTime": 52.8407480558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "順調そうだな。雫はよく頑張ってると思うよ\n座長としても、役者としても",
      "startTime": 59.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "実は演技……すみれちゃんに頼んで、見てもらってる\n『ぱじゃパ！』がきっかけで、仲良くなったから",
      "startTime": 67.8827433904,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}